Then in part three we’ll explore the aftermath of Hiroshima and Nagasaki,

00:16:46.190 --> 00:16:49.910
discuss some of the ethical questions that have been raised about

00:16:49.930 --> 00:16:53.860
the atomic bomb, and look at how the world has changed since then.

